text: Bangalaia angolensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1938. It is known from Angola.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia angolensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1938
